body: "## Charter\nLiving capability epic for schema, config, and universal customization — the \"any kind of project\" pillar: custom item types/statuses/fields, per-type workflows, governance presets, project profiles/archetypes, and pm config keys.\n\n## Scope\n- In: pm schema family (add/remove-type, add/remove-status, add-field), per-type allowed-transitions, governance settings, profile apply (pm-kanban exemplar), init type-presets, config set key surface.\n- Out: extension-registered types' runtime loading (pm-ugqx), settings-file write concurrency (pm-bgcu under pm-dj98).\n\n## Status\n23 closed children (schema epic completion plan pm-z5nb largely delivered: remove-type, add-status, per-type workflows, create_default_type; profiles PR#362/364; kanban archetype PR#367). Open children:\n- pm-28cf — search config normalization GH-244 follow-up (empty provider/adapter strings should auto-normalize).\n- pm-z5nb — completion Plan retained open as the epic's verification checklist; close after confirming every referenced child is closed and documented."
